measurements.description: Fourteen flowers on two up to 35-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals round, flat, slight fenestrations between dorsal sepal and petals, white overlaid dark purple spots coalescing at distal edges; lip white, side lobes overlaid light purple, midlobe overlaid dark purple, throat dark purple stripes; column white blushed pink centrally, anther cap yellow; substance firm; texture crystalline.
